          "body": {
            "text": "A new guide covering Tumbo, Simonsberget, Bistaberget, and other crags in Södermanland was released in November 2006. Order via www.dangerzone.se.\n\nA free version of the Tumbo guide can be found here (http://www.klattring.net/?p=341).",
